texts.html: HOUSTON (AP)  Miami tight end Dustin Keller sustained what appears to be a serious right leg injury in the second quarter against the Houston Texans.
text: HOUSTON (AP)  Miami tight end Dustin Keller sustained what appears to be a serious right leg injury in the second quarter against the Houston Texans.

texts.html: Keller's leg bent unnaturally when he was tackled on the right knee by D.J. Swearinger on an incomplete pass Saturday night. He immediately grabbed his right knee and was soon carted off the field.
text: Keller's leg bent unnaturally when he was tackled on the right knee by D.J. Swearinger on an incomplete pass Saturday night. He immediately grabbed his right knee and was soon carted off the field.

texts.html: Dolphins coach Joe Philbin said he didn't have a diagnosis on Keller's injury, but wide receiver Mike Wallace was preparing for the worst.
text: Dolphins coach Joe Philbin said he didn't have a diagnosis on Keller's injury, but wide receiver Mike Wallace was preparing for the worst.

texts.html: "It looked pretty bad, and I'm pretty sure he's going to be out for a while," Wallace said, adding that he hadn't heard anything official on Keller's status.
text: "It looked pretty bad, and I'm pretty sure he's going to be out for a while," Wallace said, adding that he hadn't heard anything official on Keller's status.

texts.html: Keller spent his first five seasons with the New York Jets before signing with the Dolphins in the offseason.
text: Keller spent his first five seasons with the New York Jets before signing with the Dolphins in the offseason.

texts.html: He had one reception for 14 yards on Saturday.

texts.html: Texans rookie WR Hopkins leaves game with head injury
text: Texans rookie WR Hopkins leaves game with head injury

texts.html: HOUSTON (AP)  Houston first-round pick receiver DeAndre Hopkins left the Texans' game against Miami because of a head injury.
text: HOUSTON (AP)  Houston first-round pick receiver DeAndre Hopkins left the Texans' game against Miami because of a head injury.

texts.html: It was unclear when he was injured, but he was taken to the locker room to be evaluated in the second quarter and the team said he wouldn't return. No further details on his injury were immediately available.
text: It was unclear when he was injured, but he was taken to the locker room to be evaluated in the second quarter and the team said he wouldn't return. No further details on his injury were immediately available.

texts.html: Texans coach Gary Kubiak said he wasn't sure how Hopkins was injured, but saw him looking disoriented on the field.
text: Texans coach Gary Kubiak said he wasn't sure how Hopkins was injured, but saw him looking disoriented on the field.

texts.html: "He didn't run the route, didn't get his depth, was just stumbling all over the place," Kubiak said. "So we got him out."
text: "He didn't run the route, didn't get his depth, was just stumbling all over the place," Kubiak said. "So we got him out."

texts.html: Hopkins, the 27th overall pick this year out of Clemson, had two receptions for 22 yards before leaving the game.

texts.html: ALAMEDA, Calif. (AP)  Oakland Raiders first-round cornerback D.J. Hayden has been cleared for contact for the first time since a near-fatal heart injury almost ended his career last November.
text: ALAMEDA, Calif. (AP)  Oakland Raiders first-round cornerback D.J. Hayden has been cleared for contact for the first time since a near-fatal heart injury almost ended his career last November.

texts.html: That news couldn't come at a better time for the Raiders.
text: That news couldn't come at a better time for the Raiders.

texts.html: Starting cornerback Tracy Porter injured his groin Friday night and will likely be sidelined this week and the rest of the defense failed to stop Drew Brees and the New Orleans Saints' first-team offense even once.
